{"tid":2207613,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美大使晤台處長 撐參與聯國","createTime":"2020-09-18T09:36:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-18T10:59:07.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"22906281f735f62441ab4c329ff56f3372d3d09d","tid":2207613,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T09:36:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200918/QPALSKY7HNBOZJ5AYGU6FVOE5M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200918%2FQPALSKY7HNBOZJ5AYGU6FVOE5M%2F&d=U3in%2BbByR8w%2FZmejrHnAddjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=4ba5fb57\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200918%2FQPALSKY7HNBOZJ5AYGU6FVOE5M%2F&h=a209639c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200918/QPALSKY7HNBOZJ5AYGU6FVOE5M/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n美大使晤台處長 撐參與聯國<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/7MTIwSINIrN6JlLJAwrofuYBZwo=/877x567/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XIY2JCA6AVE4BNUIDLLHBJT4IU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F7MTIwSINIrN6JlLJAwrofuYBZwo%3D%2F877x567%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXIY2JCA6AVE4BNUIDLLHBJT4IU.jpg&h=67b9580f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國駐聯合國大使克拉夫特（Kelly Craft）前日與台灣駐紐約台北經濟文化辦事處處長李光章共晉午餐（圖）。克拉夫特表示，這次會晤具「歷史性」意義，承諾將協助台灣參與聯合國事務，希望未來能與蔡英文會晤。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n稱為港台挺身抗北京<br />\n<br />\n兩人在紐約曼哈頓一間戶外餐廳共晉午餐。克拉夫特說，台灣應該要能夠像所有其他國家一樣參與聯合國事務，「如果美國不為台灣挺身對抗中國，那麼誰會挺身而出？不只台灣，還有香港」。她又稱，2,400萬台灣民眾「必須被聽見，而他們遭到北京邊緣化」，她強調美國與台灣有促進民主的共同目標，希望有朝一日能與蔡英文會晤。李光章則向美聯社表示：「台灣與美國在民主、人權、法治方面有共同價值觀，我們可以成為偉大夥伴。」<br />\n<br />\n美聯社分析，美國與民主台灣的關係近來升溫，國會兩黨強烈支持，也顯示特。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n台灣自1971年退出聯合國，被排除在所有聯合國旗下機構外。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n台灣蘋果新聞網"},{"pid":"25397c983f55406ad663b9f0e9bb22ed0e2997ed","tid":2207613,"uid":121146,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T09:39:04.000Z","msg":"美國已經撐台撐到入聯合國   支共都唔敢反枱  我真係笑撚左<br />\n證明黑狗馬全個亞洲政策都錯撚哂  <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fb927319680f3e9cbf8a360b7a145d380910247","tid":2207613,"uid":46356,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"25397c983f55406ad663b9f0e9bb22ed0e2997ed","tid":2207613,"uid":121146,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T09:39:04.000Z","msg":"美國已經撐台撐到入聯合國   支共都唔敢反枱  我真係笑撚左<br />\n證明黑狗馬全個亞洲政策都錯撚哂  <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T10:16:28.000Z","msg":"但始終老共o係聯合國有否決權<br />\n台灣入聯基本上冇乜可能唔會被ban喎"},{"pid":"aea15adbe2f6dd8c390273144bc24194b0f1df06","tid":2207613,"uid":84926,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T10:20:31.000Z","msg":"好嬲好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中國手足已成condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf3479016161c8a4491d645fae5a225eed0b802f","tid":2207613,"uid":121146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4fb927319680f3e9cbf8a360b7a145d380910247","tid":2207613,"uid":46356,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"25397c983f55406ad663b9f0e9bb22ed0e2997ed","tid":2207613,"uid":121146,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T09:39:04.000Z","msg":"美國已經撐台撐到入聯合國   支共都唔敢反枱  我真係笑撚左<br />\n證明黑狗馬全個亞洲政策都錯撚哂  <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/so